1
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:11,220
♪Dark clouds shroud the long trail
where the sun descends♪

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,980
♪Must we only meet by chance
and never again?♪

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,900
♪To be parted forever in an instant♪

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:19,660
♪The sighs of passing years♪

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,700
♪When your smile is embedded
in the starry night♪

6
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:25,740
♪We are puppets of twisted fates♪

7
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,620
♪Constantly intertwining♪

8
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:31,660
♪Dissolving in the crowd♪

9
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,940
♪Perhaps out of reach and out of sight♪

10
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:37,260
♪Constantly flashing through my dreams♪

11
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:45,100
♪The sudden icy wind blurs my vision♪

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:50,660
♪The rain drew that day to an end♪

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:54,380
♪How I wish your beauty♪

14
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:59,460
♪I want to love you,
love you, love you, love you♪

15
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:10,860
[My Divine Emissary]

16
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,980
[Episode 6]

17
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:17,180
Then it seems your love for His Majesty

18
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:18,860
is less than your love for silver.

19
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:19,900
Of course.

20
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:21,380
Career's the most important thing.

21
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:25,180
His Majesty
will have to rank after money.

22
00:01:30,180 --> 00:01:32,340
Your Majesty, I'll take my leave.

23
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:34,180
So, I'm only placed second.

24
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:43,420
Why...?

25
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,820
Weren't you a smarty pants

26
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:46,980
when you were using me
to make money?

27
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:48,740
Why aren't you talking now?

28
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:51,860
It's all a misunderstanding.

29
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:54,580
My loyalty to Your Majesty
can be proven by the heavens.

30
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:57,580
Lu Huan.

31
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,140
Yes.

32
00:01:58,540 --> 00:01:59,580
- Confiscate all the money.
- Huh?

33
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:00,580
Yes.

34
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:04,140
Li Mengmeng,

35
00:02:05,980 --> 00:02:07,180
I want to be placed first.

36
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:17,420
Luckily I escaped quickly.

37
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,060
If anyone finds out

38
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,620
that I'm with a little eunuch every day,

39
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,980
my reputation will be tarnished.

40
00:02:20,980 --> 00:02:22,180
[Eunuch Quarters]

41
00:02:27,860 --> 00:02:28,500
Are you alright?

42
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:31,380
Stop feigning kindness,

43
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:32,900
why are you chasing me?

44
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:34,180
You were acting suspicious

45
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:35,420
while running out
of the Eunuch Quarters.

46
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,860
Is it a crime if I acted suspiciously?

47
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:38,860
Sorry,

48
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:39,580
you started running

49
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,660
and I chased you out of habit.

50
00:02:48,940 --> 00:02:49,420
Take this.

51
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,220
What is it?

52
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:54,100
This is a healing ointment
granted by His Majesty.

53
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:54,660
It's...

54
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:58,540
really effective.

55
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:05,100
Your Majesty.

56
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:11,020
Hey, please don't be angry anymore!

57
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:12,860
I gave you all my money.

58
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:14,740
Do you have more objections?

59
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:15,980
Yes, indeed.

60
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:18,460
I've cheered for you in court

61
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:20,020
until my voice...

62
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,620
became hoarse.

63
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:24,980
Helped me?

64
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,580
It seems like
you're helping your purse.

65
00:03:28,060 --> 00:03:28,940
Your Majesty,

66
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:30,700
I've learned from my mistake.

67
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,620
Please forgive me.

68
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:41,060
Or, I can cook for you

69
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:42,180
a delicacy from my hometown.

70
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:43,580
After you're well-fed,

71
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:45,380
your anger will dissipate as well.

72
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:48,540
What will it be?

73
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:53,340
You'll get to know soon.

74
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:00,980
Are you sure this is edible?

75
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:02,180
Not only is it edible,

76
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:04,060
it's very delicious too.

77
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:07,140
Why are you cooking the flour
with cold water?

78
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,300
Will it be cooked?

79
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,660
Steward Lu,

80
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:11,020
don't you know?

81
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,380
The flour soaked in cold water

82
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,500
will be smoother
and it'll be more elastic.

83
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:17,180
Elastic?

84
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:22,900
Fan the fire.

85
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:30,620
Remove the lid.

86
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:44,420
What smell is that?

87
00:04:45,340 --> 00:04:46,740
It's sourish and smelly.

88
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:49,980
Are you sure
you want to give this to His Majesty?

89
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,460
What do you mean
by it's sourish and smelly?

90
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:54,420
This is one of the most

91
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:56,420
popular delicacies in my hometown.

92
00:04:57,460 --> 00:05:01,700
Take one bite and you won't forget it.

93
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:03,740
No, thank you.

94
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:06,620
I may not give it to you.

95
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:07,340
What a waste!

96
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,460
Even for a man,

97
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,860
isn't this room a bit too messy?

98
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:42,900
Don't move!

99
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:48,820
Come, come.

100
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:49,820
Sit over there.

101
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,140
I left in a hurry

102
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:52,900
and didn't have the time to clean up.

103
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:57,020
Are you hiding

104
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:58,500
some sort of treasure from me?

105
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:00,820
No, no.

106
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,180
It's only some dirty clothes.

107
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:04,140
Your Majesty's body is priceless.

108
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,980
How can I let you
touch my dirty clothes,

109
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:06,540
am I right?

110
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:13,100
Come,

111
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,340
give my cooking a try.

112
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:17,060
I'd like to see what you made

113
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:19,340
that had me waiting for so long.

114
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:28,180
What is it?

115
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:32,700
Did you not say

116
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,980
you'll make a delicacy
from your hometown?

117
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,140
Why does it smell like feces?

118
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,020
What do you mean by feces?

119
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:42,020
This is called snail rice noodles.

120
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,780
Although it's smelly,

121
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,900
but it's delicious.

122
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,380
Give it a try.

123
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:48,740
Come, come.

124
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,420
I will not eat this.

125
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,420
Are you sure?

126
00:06:58,900 --> 00:06:59,500
Yes.

127
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:00,660
Your Majesty,

128
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,540
are you scared of eating it?

129
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:07,740
How is it?

130
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,380
It's delicious, right?

131
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:15,260
Your Majesty.

132
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:19,580
Your Majesty.

133
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,580
Your Majesty.

134
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:24,860
Hey.

135
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:27,180
Hey.

136
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,740
Your Majesty.

137
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:32,940
Your Majesty, wake up.

138
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:40,140
Oh, no!

139
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,620
I'll be beheaded this time.

140
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,620
Your Majesty!

141
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:48,820
Your Majesty,

142
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:49,900
it's late.

143
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:50,980
It's time to return to the palace.

144
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:57,060
Oh, no!

145
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,500
Qi Yan is dead in my room.

146
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:00,020
I'll definitely get beheaded.

147
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:11,740
Oh, no!

148
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:13,500
I'm sure to get caught.

149
00:08:16,420 --> 00:08:17,820
How dare you, audacious slave!

150
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:19,540
You killed His Majesty
with that stinky food.

151
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,100
This is treason!

152
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:22,180
Off with her head!

153
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:28,460
No!

154
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,860
I'm sure to die this time.

155
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,020
What if, I try again?

156
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:41,540
I guess I have no choice.

157
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:53,940
Your Majesty,

158
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:56,620
when I first met you,

159
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:58,620
I really hated you.

160
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:01,980
Because you always threatened me
by saying you'll behead me.

161
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:05,860
But after a while,

162
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,260
I noticed

163
00:09:07,260 --> 00:09:09,140
you're not a tyrant.

164
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:11,380
I'm sorry.

165
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:13,660
You're still so young.

166
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:14,420
Yet,

167
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:18,420
you got stink to death
by the snail rice noodles.

168
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:20,900
I know it's too late

169
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,220
to apologize now.

170
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:23,900
If

171
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,700
there's an afterlife,

172
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:28,420
I'll make it up to you then.

173
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,020
Your Majesty,

174
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:33,980
goodbye.

175
00:09:46,540 --> 00:09:47,420
Li Mengmeng.

176
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,220
Li Mengmeng.

177
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,580
Li Mengmeng.

178
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,700
I was only playing a prank on you

179
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:08,420
for always making me angry.

180
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:11,100
Who plays such a prank?

181
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:12,940
So, only you are allowed to lie to me,

182
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,180
and I'm not allowed to do the same?

183
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,700
You can't joke with your life.

184
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,540
I told you it's not funny.

185
00:10:26,420 --> 00:10:27,260
Summon the imperial physician.

186
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:29,660
Hurry!

187
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:39,300
[Qingyan Palace]

188
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:56,700
Your Majesty,

189
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:57,660
are you awake?

190
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,340
I'll summon the imperial physician over.

191
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:00,140
There's no need for it.

192
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:01,900
I'm fine.

193
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,100
Where is Eunuch Li?

194
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:05,820
Your Majesty.

195
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:08,020
How can you still be worried
about that traitor?

196
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,940
If he wasn't instructed by Prince Heqin,

197
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:11,980
you would not have eaten

198
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,340
that food with peanuts in it.

199
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:15,460
And you would not have fallen ill.

200
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:18,260
Are you saying Prince Heqin?

201
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:22,020
Your Majesty,

202
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:22,980
please have a look.

203
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:45,980
Do you need to be that far away from me?

204
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:47,580
Come closer.

205
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:54,500
Come over here!

206
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:08,180
Is this Prince Heqin?

207
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:12,860
No.

208
00:12:13,260 --> 00:12:14,420
This is Bai Lian.

209
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:15,740
He's someone from my hometown.

210
00:12:15,740 --> 00:12:16,380
Nonsense!

211
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,060
He looks exactly

212
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:20,100
like Prince Heqin.

213
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:22,100
This...

214
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:24,620
I couldn't explain it either.

215
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:28,260
How about this?

216
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:29,900
Are you deliberately trying

217
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,340
to poison me with peanuts?

218
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:32,300
Peanuts?

219
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:35,380
Are peanuts poisonous?

220
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:40,060
Are you allergic to peanuts?

221
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:41,980
Then what about this?

222
00:12:44,340 --> 00:12:44,940
This...

223
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:53,820
Your Majesty,

224
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:58,220
this thing is amazing.

225
00:12:58,620 --> 00:13:00,220
Once I use it on you,

226
00:13:00,860 --> 00:13:03,180
things will work out for us.

227
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:08,380
This belongs to the Noble Consort.

228
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,580
She asked me to keep it for her

229
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:12,100
when she left the palace.

230
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:13,780
The Noble Consort?

231
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:19,300
Open it for me.

232
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,980
Why is it happening again?

233
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,420
Bring my ointment for me.

234
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:52,460
It's on the table.

235
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:53,660
Alright.

236
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:29,340
Your Majesty.

237
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:40,380
She's...a girl?

238
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,340
Your Majesty...

239
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:09,740
Oh, no!

240
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,020
How will I face King Yama in the future?

241
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,180
Your Majesty.

242
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:15,020
Your Majesty...

243
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:20,620
Eunuch Li, I'm coming in.

244
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:21,220
Who is it?

245
00:15:23,180 --> 00:15:23,980
Oh, no!

246
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:25,460
Is he really here to catch me?

247
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:28,820
What are you doing?

248
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:29,740
His Majesty ordered

249
00:15:29,740 --> 00:15:30,940
it is unlucky and unsafe

250
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:31,940
to place this urn in the room.

251
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:34,180
To prevent Eunuch Li
from committing suicide again,

252
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:35,060
we shall take away the urn.

253
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,260
I didn't plan to use the urn
for committing suicide,

254
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,740
I left it in the room

255
00:15:37,740 --> 00:15:39,180
because I was afraid
that others would use the water in it.

256
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:42,180
There's no need to take these away.

257
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:44,420
I'm not planning to commit suicide,

258
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:45,580
return the scissors to me!

259
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:51,740
[Eunuch Quarters]

260
00:15:51,740 --> 00:15:52,420
Forget it!

261
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:54,300
Since I cannot return through the urn.

262
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:56,260
But he must return the scissors to me.

263
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:02,020
I gained a lot
from this official business trip.

264
00:16:07,780 --> 00:16:11,100
Please let it rain!

265
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:15,420
Isn't he the...

266
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:16,940
high priest from the other day?

267
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:20,580
Did anything happen
in the Lingtai Pavilion recently?

268
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,780
High priest, everything is normal

269
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:23,500
while you're not around.

270
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,260
That day he stood so close to me

271
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:26,300
on the altar,

272
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:28,380
it would be bad if he recognized me.

273
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:36,300
What are you doing?

274
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:38,100
Hurry to the hall to assemble.

275
00:16:38,460 --> 00:16:39,540
Yes.

276
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:45,940
How is it him?

277
00:16:53,860 --> 00:16:54,900
What is going on?

278
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,060
This is a eunuch assessment
for new recruits

279
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:57,540
that is held every 6 months.

280
00:16:59,020 --> 00:17:00,660
Eunuchs need to be assessed?

281
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:01,700
Of course.

282
00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:06,380
Recently, someone has disguised
as a eunuch

283
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:08,660
and did things
that have greatly tarnished

284
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:10,420
our reputations.

285
00:17:10,740 --> 00:17:12,180
Remember this,

286
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:14,100
when working in the palace,

287
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:15,340
